Some of you tried a little too hard, cover letters, life stories-n-shit. So I couldn’t choose. 
•
If you live in SYDNEY Check your email tonight for a zoom link. We’re meeting this Thursday at 8:00pm (Sydney time)
•
To everyone else who commented and messaged, you showed me there is plenty of interest for this, I’m limited in the zoom attendees so we’ll have to do another session once I iron out the kinks. I’ll notify you here on Insta when  we are ready to go again.
